OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782906492
OL,3,CWimbledon prepares for hotter summers
OL,4,Cafter record-breaking heatwave
OL,6,FMr Stubley said: "Two male players
OL,7,F(Novak Djokovic and Jannik Sinner) are
OL,8,Fnotorious for sliding into their
OL,9,Fshots, so that means that tears into
OL,10,Fthe turf.
OL,12,F"When you've got Jannik going into
OL,13,Ffive sets or Novak going into four
OL,14,Fsets, there's probably three sets
OL,15,Fthere that I wasn't expecting
OL,16,Fyesterday, which now we have to manage
OL,17,Ffor the rest of the championships.
OL,26,@nD@ROUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782906492
OL,3,CWimbledon prepares for hotter summers
OL,4,Cafter record-breaking heatwave
OL,6,F"Whereas if you look at today's
OL,7,Fschedule, we have two ladies' and the
OL,8,Fmen's, so when you look at the end of
OL,9,Fday two, you've probably evened out."
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FMr Stubley said he enjoys that each of
OL,17,Fhis 31 championships has been
OL,18,Fdifferent.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
