FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782906492
OL,3,CWimbledon prepares for hotter summers
OL,4,Cafter record-breaking heatwave
OL,6,FHe said: "I quite like the pressure,
OL,7,Fand the fact that we have to showcase
OL,8,Four courts to the world every year, so
OL,9,Fit's quite nice to have that labour of
OL,10,Flove that all year, you're doing a
OL,11,Fjob, and then you can just show
OL,12,Feverybody what we've done.
OL,14,F"But then you're then on the roller
OL,15,Fcoaster journey for the two weeks.
OL,17,F"You constantly have a knot in your
OL,18,Fstomach, but it's a kind of a happy
OL,19,Fknot, because you're as nervous as you
OL,20,Fare excited, so it's a 50-50 of the
OL,21,Fboth.
OL,26,@nD@JOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782906492
OL,3,CWimbledon prepares for hotter summers
OL,4,Cafter record-breaking heatwave
OL,6,F"That's probably the most scrutinised
OL,7,Fpiece of turf in the world, in Centre
OL,8,FCourt, so to be in charge of it, and
OL,9,Feventually hand it over to somebody
OL,10,Felse for them to have a go and take it
OL,11,Fto the next stage that we've got it to
OL,12,Fat the moment, it's nice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@ZO]
